dct_title_s: GIS data for the Watersheds mapping series, map set 1, Noyo River Watershed
dct_alternative_sm: Watershed mapping series, Noyo River Watershed, map set 1
dct_description_sm: Results of Noyo River Watershed Landslide Mapping Project, including geologic and geomorphic features (landslide) maps and landslide potential maps.
by Michael W. Manson, Julie A. Sowma-Bawcom, and Timothy K. Parker.
Graphics files for all 6 maps in the set (in .pdf, .rft, .gra formats), Arcinfo export files, Arcview shape files, and coverage metadata, as well as Acrobat Reader.

System requirements: Intel Pentium processor; Microsoft Windows 95 OSR 2.0, Windows 98 SE, Windows Millennium, Windows NT 4.0 with Service Pack 5, or Windows 2000; 64 MB of RAM; 24 MB of available hard-disk space; Adobe Acrobat Reader 5.
